  "detailed_description": "A rogue-like pirate adventure game.<br><br>Explore a skeleton-riddled archipelago in search of a giant monster. Follow treasure maps and hints to items, weapons and secrets. Can you defeat the terrible kraken?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>fun combat mechanics<br></li><li>ships, cannons and rafts<br></li><li>funny legs<br></li><li>randomly generated map - different each time you play!<br></li><li>6+ treasures to find<br></li><li>about 1+ hour of play time</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206720/extras/a7aa21568f1ec851e11b7e967b40cafc.poster.avif?t=1639495476\" width=560 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206720/extras/a7aa21568f1ec851e11b7e967b40cafc.webm?t=1639495476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206720/extras/a7aa21568f1ec851e11b7e967b40cafc.mp4?t=1639495476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>X to grab<br></li><li>Z to use item / shoot cannon<br></li><li>C to swap item / cannon side</li></ul><br>Also playable with controller.<br><br>Special thanks to Joanne for the voice-acting!<br><br><i>Note: the game is not saved when you quit or restart!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206720/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1639495476\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
